flowchart TD
  S([Request Tata masuk]):::start --> T{Jenis request?}
  T -->|Typo/bug| BUG[Kakashi: assign owner -> fix]
  T -->|Tanya/status| ASK[Nami: jawab status]
  T -->|Fitur/produk| PM[Lelouch PM: intake + probing]
  PM --> C1{Masalah jelas?}
  C1 -->|Tidak| PM
  C1 -->|Ya| FR[Lelouch: frame problem + metrik]
  FR --> C2{Butuh riset?}
  C2 -->|Ya| RD[Senku R&D: riset/POC]
  RD --> SC[Lelouch: scope + prioritas]
  C2 -->|Tidak| SC
  SC --> KO[Kickoff Triad:<br/>Lelouch+Bulma+Kakashi]
  KO --> C3{Arsitektur besar?}
  C3 -->|Ya| AR[Sogeking: target arch + ADR]
  AR --> DS[Bulma: desain UX+UI + responsive]
  C3 -->|Tidak| DS
  DS --> FE[Killua: feasibility check]
  FE --> C4{Feasible + sign-off?}
  C4 -->|Tidak| DS
  C4 -->|Ya| BUILD[Build paralel:<br/>Killua FE + Saitama BE + Shikamaru DBA]
  BUILD --> QA[L: QA + edge case]
  QA --> C5{Lolos QA?}
  C5 -->|Tidak| BUILD
  C5 -->|Ya| GATE[Kakashi: Pre-Tata Gate]
  GATE --> C6{Gate PASS?}
  C6 -->|Tidak| DS
  C6 -->|Ya| TATA{Tata sign-off?}
  TATA -->|Revisi| PM
  TATA -->|Approve| DEP[Levi: deploy]
  DEP --> OUT([Fitur LIVE]):::done
  classDef start fill:#a87fb8,color:#fff,stroke:#6b4779
  classDef done fill:#6b8454,color:#fff,stroke:#3f5230
